n in the water column. This rise in 34S is not accompanied by an increase in $\delta$OSO418, which could reflect a change in either the oxidation mechanism of SO4 or an oceanic fluctuation in $\delta$18O. {\textcopyright} 2005 Elsevier B.V. All rights reserved.},
